ps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/mercury-prize-2023-comp-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/mercury-prize-2023-comp-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2023 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">水星奖</a>提名已揭晓， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arctic-monkeys">Arctic Monkeys</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/j-hus">J Hus</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">RAYE</a>入围。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-wins-the-2022-mercury-prize-for-sometimes-i-might-be-introvert-3331258">Little Simz 凭借《有时我可能内向》荣获 2022 年水星奖</a></strong></li></ul><p>该奖项的获奖者将于 9 月 7 日在伦敦 Eventim Apollo 举行的现场颁奖典礼上宣布，并由包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anna-calvi">Anna Calvi</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-cullum">Jamie Cullum</a> 、Mistajam 等在内的评审团进行评审。</p><p>提名名单上的其他人包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/loyle-carner">Loyle Carner</a> （他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/loyle-carner-hugo-review-an-honest-unflashy-storyteller-3332632">《Hugo》</a>专辑）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jockstrap">Jockstrap</a> （首张唱片<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jockstrap-i-love-you-jennifer-b-review-radar-3305709">《I Love You Jennifer B》</a> ）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/young-fathers">Young Fathers</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/young-fathers-heavy-heavy-review-3389936">《Heavy Heavy》</a> ）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-again">Fred Again..</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/fred-again-actual-life-3-review-3336600">《Actual Life 3》） （2022 年 1 月 1 日至 9 月 9 日”</a> ）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jessie-ware">Jessie Ware</a> （<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jessie-ware-that-feels-good-album-review-pearls-3434741">“那！感觉很好！”</a> ）。</p><p>该名单还包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-dean">Olivia Dean</a>的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/oliv